summary: This is just a merged version of \"CharGen Morphs v1-2-0\" with \"Vampire Face Less Sunken Cheeks\".
descriptionHtml:
This is just a merged version of Expired and Nuskas \"CharGen Morphs v1-2-0\" with Devacore\'s \"Vampire Face No Sunken Cheeks\". This will make the female vampire lords have the same face morph as before they became vampires. Sliders for changing face features on my vampire lord in Racemenu works for me at least.

This works exactly as the Chargen Morphs on the CharGen Extension page. This is an replacement for that one if you want the unsunken female vampire face instead of the vanilla morph. Install with NMM.
From the CharGen file page:
\"Morph set by Nuska. Adds 13-14 extra morphs for both genders of all nonbeast races.\"

Got many replies from people not sure how to do this on their own so uploaded my edit, but if Devacore wants me to remove it I will do so.

To make this I have used the files from:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36925/?]Chargen Extension[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/16506/?]Vampire Face Less Sunken Cheeks[/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30162/?]Animation Tools N2 - edit TRI files[/url]

Since I haven\'t made any content and merely repackaged this, I\'m not seeking any credit of my own. All credit goes to the original authors. I got the permissions from Expired and Nuska for releasing this.

Update:
A new version for 1.2.2 for ECE users was added to optional files.
author: Expired-Nuska-Devacore
